  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Garment exports for the second month dom. More than 500",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Board of Investment says that in July, Sri Lanka's garment export revenue has crossed the 500 million US dollar mark for the second month in a row.",
        "Sri Lanka's garment export revenue in June was 536.65 million US dollars and in July the same revenue was recorded as 522.13 million dollars.",
        "Considering the first 7 months of this year, the country's garment export revenue has exceeded 3.3 billion US dollars. In 2021, Sri Lanka earned US$ 5.4 billion from garment exports."
      ],
